  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "We've implemented the latest proposal in the latest beta of instantsearch.js v2. It works fine except that now it poses problem for custom widget that want to bind on the help lifecycle as well. This is because of the behavior of an event emitter behavior as a prototype (with the use of immutable objects which don't update their values in place). see #2176 ",
